{"tid":1439172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［咪撚影相啊屌你］大埔副本新嘗試，必入！","createTime":"2019-08-10T04:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:45:16.000Z","uid":226413,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2554216863d8101a81dabc56abaa7a4ac612751","tid":1439172,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"以往大家都想保護手足，叫人唔好影相<br />\n但往往無可能勸阻到所有人，更無可能短時間內令街坊明白，影相會傷害到示威者<br />\n除左刻意大頭之外，今日不如包實啲自己，好過周街屌人老母影相<br />\n<br />\n1. 頭巾遮臉遮耳，又無咁熱<br />\n2. 太陽眼鏡<br />\n3. 鞋要用膠紙貼住<br />\n4. 背囊logo要封好<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實做齊以上幾樣，影你都唔驚</span></strong><br />\n引用律師朋友既說話: 如果唔係當場拘捕，你又唔係淨戴個口罩，基本上證明唔到你就係當事人，所以一定要包實<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤 不散</span></span>"},{"pid":"83e49be87d3f00946b1b5ab9ae9792f1b5bc677b","tid":1439172,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"推十連"},{"pid":"72a5c3f66f063a7043546af53f21510514bd4f75","tid":1439172,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b292751bcc3dd873a0d405770ef2493bd0607d31","tid":1439172,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:27:45.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"3012b3c2aa4970e548768c8a2e40871e59314987","tid":1439172,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:28:12.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"88c8fe140ffe7d8ca207e164dfd73d0aa66462d7","tid":1439172,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"e25c6283d5648afd73875a005e89dc8ce78ab880","tid":1439172,"uid":303143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"自己包實啲好過屌人地影你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d519b6c5b617cce6f67b03817540b81b0f2630","tid":1439172,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike"